        <p class="lead">To search for news articles simply enter them in the search bar below and click search
          button. If the term
          has multiple words in it you are free to use regular spaces to seperate them.
          <br>
          In addition if you are looking for articles on different topics at the same time, you can type them in the
          search bar at the same time, just seperate them with a
          comma. <br>
          Example:"Fist Subject,Second Subject."
          <br>
          This will bring up news articles for both subjects
          from all available sources
          <br>
          Currently there is a limit to how many seperate subjects you can search for. Even if you pass in 100 different
          comma seperated expressions, there will only be 3-4 unique requests</p>
